    faqs: [{"id":"faq-0","question":"What is your pricing model?","answer":"We offer flexible pricing models designed to fit organizations of any size. Choose from per-user monthly or annual subscriptions, per-transaction pricing for usage-based billing, or custom enterprise licensing with volume discounts. All plans include core features, regular updates, and standard support. Annual billing saves up to 20%, and we offer special pricing for nonprofits and educational institutions. Contact our sales team for a custom quote tailored to your needs."},{"id":"faq-1","question":"Are there hidden fees?","answer":"Absolutely not. We believe in complete pricing transparency with no hidden fees, setup charges, or surprise costs. The price you see is the price you pay, and it includes all platform updates, security patches, and standard support. Volume discounts are available for larger teams, and annual billing provides additional savings of up to 20%. We will always notify you in advance if any pricing changes are planned."},{"id":"faq-2","question":"Can we try before buying?","answer":"Absolutely. We offer a full-featured free trial with no credit card required and no feature limitations. During the trial period, you get access to the complete platform including all premium features, integrations, and dedicated onboarding support. Our team will help you set up the trial environment to match your real workflows, so you can evaluate TrackNexus with your actual data and processes before making a commitment."},{"id":"faq-3","question":"What security certifications do you have?","answer":"TrackNexus holds SOC 2 Type II, ISO 27001, GDPR, and HIPAA compliance certifications, validated through annual independent audits. We also maintain compliance with CCPA, PCI DSS for payment processing, and industry-specific regulations. Our security team continuously monitors the regulatory landscape and implements updates proactively. Detailed compliance documentation and audit reports are available upon request for your review."}],
